latestIgtvVideos.title: First Impressions : Dyson Airwrap @dyson_india
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hii! The amount of people that were DMinng me over this week about the @dyson_india Airwrap was totally insane so I decided to post this ASAP for y’all! 💕
✨To start with, I’m really happy with all the attachments that I used here, they were amazing to work with and so fun!
✨The Airwrap barrels took some time to get used to because if you have longer hair you cannot be using big chunks or the hair will get left out from wrapping around the barrels!
✨It’s definitely a learning curve but I was super impressed with the kind of curls I got in the end and BOY! The volume? INSANE! If you get a good deal on this baby, definitely pick it up!

latestIgtvVideos.title: Try on : @iliabeauty Super Skin Serum with SPF 40 ✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
It’s been a couple days since I filmed this video and by now I’ve used the @iliabeauty Serum with SPF multiple times! 💕
I love how you do not need a lot of this but it does take a little effort to blend in! I’ve tried using this with a brush which I prefer. 
I’m actually surprised by it’s longevity! By the end of my work day, I’ve experienced it being fresh and it doesn’t really slip off like other tinted complexion products do! 😅

Easy hair refresh on my super gross day 3 hair with my trustyyy @dyson curl id. You’d scream if you saw my roots up close but the round brush adds so much volume so you probably can’t even see what an oily mess it actually is hehe. 
Tip : you can use a dry shampoo/texturising spray towards the end but i hate the feeling of anything other than hair serum in my hair so I just avoid.
